                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="66v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/44700813" xml:lang="en">Bedersi, Abraham ben Isaac</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/44700813" xml:lang="he">בדרשי, אברהם בן יצחק</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Igrot, shirim u-melitsot</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אגרות שירים ומליצות</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The correspondence of Abraham Bedersi and Isaac Gerondi, Todros ha-Levi ben Yosef, Pinhas ha-Levi, and others. Contains also the prayer Elef alafin (folios 1r-2v) and Baḳashat ha-lamdin (folios 5r-7r) by the author, and Baḳashat ha-mamin (folios 3r-5r) by his son, Yedayah Bedersi. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="67r" to="96v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Avne shoham</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אבני שוהם</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/51253334">Ibn Sasson, Samuel ben Joseph</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/51253334">ששון, שמואל אבן</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="he">ספר אבני השוהם חברו החכם המשורר ר' שמואל בן החכם המעולה ר' יוסף ן' ששון. <locus n="67r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     </incipit>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="97r" to="119v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Igrot, shirim u-melitsot </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אגרות שירים ומליצות</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/97206765">Da Piera, Solomon ben Meshulam</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/97206765">דפירה, שלמה בן משולם</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A poetical correspondence between Don Vidal Benveniste and Solomon Da Piera, followed by a few other small pieces. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 104r-119v contain a series of letters, mostly in rhymed prose, some of which bear the signature of Solomon ben Labi (see e.g. folios 105v, 106r). </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="120r" to="123r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Azharot </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אזהרות</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en">Tsalabi, Elijah ha-Kohen</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he">צלבי, אליהו הכהן</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Imperfect at the end. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="124r" to="127v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Igrot ṿe-shirim </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אגרות ושירים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/308278133">Tamar, Menahem ben Moses </persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/308278133">תמר, מנחם בן משה</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The personal correspondence between Menahem ben Moses and certain David (perhaps David ibn Yahya, inscribed on folio 125v?). The author's signature is placed on folios 124r-124v, and in an acrostic at the beginning. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="128r" to="137v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Igrot, shirim u-melitsot </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אגרות שירים ומליצות</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/97206765" xml:lang="en">Da Piera, Solomon ben Meshulam </persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/97206765" xml:lang="he">דפירה, שלמה בן משולם</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 128-129 contain a reduplication of contents of folio 95, followed by other verses in rhymed prose by Solomon Da Piera. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
